Installation:
  Simply run the sequence of following three commands on shell
  prompt in this directory (assumes that you have write permissions
  in /usr/local to install):

  # ./configure
  # make
  # make install
 
  Alternatively, "make" in this directory will also build the mpac
  library, sample benchmarks, and copy them in target directory.

Comments are welcome.

